    • Method Detail

      • getOrder

        int getOrder()
        Gets the order.

        Use low numbers for higher priority. Normally the sorting will start from 0 and move upwards. So if you want to be last then use Integer.MAX_VALUE or eg LOWEST.

        Returns:
        the order
